  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      SR-01 may reduce facial redness. it is a topically applied product. The agent will be applied
      to local skin areas of subjects with red facial skin to assess affect, and then applied to
      the whole face to assess efficacy and safety
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
